17#include <string.h>
18
19#include <isc/net.h>

21#define RRTYPE_NID_ATTRIBUTES (0)

23static inline isc_result_t
24fromtext_nid(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
25 isc_token_t token;
26 unsigned char locator[NS_LOCATORSZ];
27
28 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_nid);
29
30 UNUSED(type);
31 UNUSED(rdclass);
32 UNUSED(origin);
33 UNUSED(options);
34 UNUSED(callbacks);
35
36 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
37 false));
38 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
39 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
40 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
41
42 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
43 false));
44
45 if (locator_pton(DNS_AS_STR(token), locator) != 1)
46 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
47 return (mem_tobuffer(target, locator, NS_LOCATORSZ));
48}
49
50static inline isc_result_t
51totext_nid(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
52 isc_region_t region;
53 char buf[sizeof("xxxx:xxxx:xxxx:xxxx")];
54 unsigned short num;
55
56 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nid);
57 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
58
59 UNUSED(tctx);
60
61 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
62 num = uint16_fromregion(&region);
63 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
64 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", num);
65 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
66
67 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
68
69 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%x:%x:%x:%x",
70 region.base[0]<<8 | region.base[1],
71 region.base[2]<<8 | region.base[3],
72 region.base[4]<<8 | region.base[5],
73 region.base[6]<<8 | region.base[7]);
74 return (str_totext(buf, target));
75}
76
77static inline isc_result_t
78fromwire_nid(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
79 isc_region_t sregion;
80
81 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_nid);
82
83 UNUSED(type);
84 UNUSED(options);
85 UNUSED(rdclass);
86 UNUSED(dctx);
87
88 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sregion);
89 if (sregion.length != 10)
90 return (DNS_R_FORMERR);
91 isc_buffer_forward(source, sregion.length);
92 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sregion.base, sregion.length));
93}
94
95static inline isc_result_t
96towire_nid(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
97
98 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nid);
99 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 10);
100
101 UNUSED(cctx);
102
103 return (mem_tobuffer(target, rdata->data, rdata->length));
104}
105
106static inline int
107compare_nid(ARGS_COMPARE) {
108 isc_region_t region1;
109 isc_region_t region2;
110
111 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
112 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
113 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_nid);
114 REQUIRE(rdata1->length == 10);
115 REQUIRE(rdata2->length == 10);
116
117 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
118 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
119 return (isc_region_compare(&region1, &region2));
120}
121
122static inline isc_result_t
123fromstruct_nid(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
124 dns_rdata_nid_t *nid = source;
125
126 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_nid);
127 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
128 REQUIRE(nid->common.rdtype == type);
129 REQUIRE(nid->common.rdclass == rdclass);
130
131 UNUSED(type);
132 UNUSED(rdclass);
133
134 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(nid->pref, target));
135 return (mem_tobuffer(target, nid->nid, sizeof(nid->nid)));
136}
137
138static inline isc_result_t
139tostruct_nid(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
140 isc_region_t region;
141 dns_rdata_nid_t *nid = target;
142
143 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nid);
144 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
145 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 10);
146
147 UNUSED(mctx);
148
149 nid->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
150 nid->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
151 ISC_LINK_INIT(&nid->common, link);
152
153 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
154 nid->pref = uint16_fromregion(&region);
155 memmove(nid->nid, region.base, region.length);
156 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
157}
158
159static inline void
160freestruct_nid(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
161 dns_rdata_nid_t *nid = source;
162
163 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
164 REQUIRE(nid->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_nid);
165
166 return;
167}

169static inline isc_result_t
170additionaldata_nid(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
171
172 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nid);
173 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 10);
174
175 UNUSED(rdata);
176 UNUSED(add);
177 UNUSED(arg);
178
179 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
180}
181
182static inline isc_result_t
183digest_nid(ARGS_DIGEST) {
184 isc_region_t r;
185
186 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nid);
187 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 10);
188
189 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
190
191 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
192}

194static inline bool
195checkowner_nid(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
196
197 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_nid);
198
199 UNUSED(name);
200 UNUSED(type);
201 UNUSED(rdclass);
202 UNUSED(wildcard);
203
204 return (true);
205}

207static inline bool
208checknames_nid(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
209
210 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_nid);
211 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 10);
212
213 UNUSED(rdata);
214 UNUSED(owner);
215 UNUSED(bad);
216
217 return (true);

220static inline int
221casecompare_nid(ARGS_COMPARE) {
222 return (compare_nid(rdata1, rdata2));
223}
